headline: PSE&G Energy Efficiency Programs Deliver More Than $900 Million in Annual Utility Bill Savings for New Jersey Customers
summary: PSE&G's latest Clean Energy Future-Energy Efficiency (CEF-EE) report demonstrates continued savings for customers across New Jersey. From program implementation beginning in October 2020 through September 2025, nearly 480,000 customers participated in PSE&G's energy efficiency programs. Collectively, that participation is delivering more than $900 million in annual customer savingsi.
